            {
              "enText": "<b>Lesson 11 • Motivating Co-Workers</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "Greg, Stan, and Donna work for Pack-It, a maker of trash bags and other consumer goods. After disappointing sales results, they discuss exiting the trash bag business. But a fresh new idea gives them hope for the"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Greg:</b> Our sales were down again last quarter."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Donna:</b> We've been <b>working our tails off</b> and our results are still lousy!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Greg:</b> Maybe we should exit the trash bag business — just <p>call it quits!</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Stan:</b> C'mon.* Let's not <b>throw in the towel</b> yet. <b>We've been down before, but we always come back fighting</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Donna:</b> But this time <b>private-label products</b> are driving us out of business!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Stan:</b> We've got a successful <b>track record</b>. Everybody knows that we offer quality trash bags."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Donna:</b> That's true, but we can't just <b>rest on our laurels</b> forever."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Stan:</b> Well, I have a new idea that's going to <b>turn around our business</b>. It's a new line of trash bags that smell like fresh fruits, such as apples and peaches."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Greg:</b> That sounds like a great idea. I'm ready to roll up my sleeves and get <b>down to business!</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Stan:</b> I appreciate your team spirit! Donna, are you on board too?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Donna:</b> Sure. <b>Count me in</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Stan:</b> Great. Let's get everybody else in the company excited about this plan too. I'll count on you two to <b>rally the troops</b>."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
